This meta-template is used to style section hatnotes which direct users to related articles.

=== Usage ===
<pre>{{rellink|1=Your text here}}</pre>
produces
{{rellink|1=Your text here}}

In most cases one won't need the <code>1=</code>, but if there's an <code>=</code> anywhere in the text provided, it is necessary.

Adding an <code>extraclasses</code> parameter allows extra CSS classes to be specified.

